6
00:01:42.910 --> 00:01:46.790
Just remember that it was you
who cast suspicion on my crew.

7
00:01:50.080 --> 00:01:56.290
Without mutual trust, we won't have
each other's backs when fighting for our lives!

8
00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:02.600
Sparks of Rebellion

9
00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:05.390
Traf was fuming when he left!

10
00:02:05.900 --> 00:02:07.460
Who knows if he'll come back.

11
00:02:08.340 --> 00:02:11.400
Shinobu went too far saying all that crap!

12
00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:14.320
You do understand what set her off, right?

13
00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:19.780
Kaido invaded her country and laid waste
to everything she had ever known,

14
00:02:19.780 --> 00:02:24.660
but she endured it for twenty years
while waiting for the moment to fight back.

15
00:02:24.660 --> 00:02:29.750
Whatever. Even if Bepo and the others had
blabbed about the plan, I wouldn't blame them.

16
00:02:29.750 --> 00:02:32.000
Sure, I mean, you'd have talked.

17
00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.420
I can say the same about you!

18
00:02:36.420 --> 00:02:38.200
Torture, huh?

19
00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:40.660
I'd last three seconds.

20
00:02:40.660 --> 00:02:42.010
Hold out longer, will you?!

21
00:02:42.010 --> 00:02:43.100
Get outta here!

22
00:02:43.890 --> 00:02:46.520
I have no business with any
of you damn peasants!

23
00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:51.190
What's going on? An angry shout
seems out of place in Ebisu Town.

24
00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:57.740
You there, old bean-washing monster granny!

25
00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:57.740
Stop it!

26
00:02:57.740 --> 00:03:03.990
They're new here. They arrived
yesterday after fleeing the capital.

27
00:03:03.990 --> 00:03:05.720
What are you looking at?!

28
00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:07.770
Get outta here, punks!

29
00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:13.500
They fled the capital?

30
00:03:13.500 --> 00:03:14.460
Yeah.

31
00:03:14.460 --> 00:03:20.590
Only those who produce wealth and show loyalty
to the shogun can live in the Flower Capital.

32
00:03:20.590 --> 00:03:26.310
I heard those men were doing
some pretty scummy things.

33
00:03:26.310 --> 00:03:27.430
First,

34
00:03:27.430 --> 00:03:29.390
we have Bungo the flunkey.
You little shits!

35
00:03:31.190 --> 00:03:34.810
Night after night, he'd roam
the streets setting fires,

36
00:03:34.810 --> 00:03:39.240
but he'd bribe officials to avoid punishment.

